OL,4,CPolish law on property stolen by Nazis
OL,5,Cangers Israel
OL,6, Poland's president Andrzej Duda has
OL,7, approved a law that will make it harder
OL,8, for Jewish people to recover property
OL,9, lost during and after World War Two.
OL,11,FIsrael has recalled its diplomatic
OL,12,Fenvoy to Warsaw over the changes,
OL,13,Fbranding the law "anti-Semitic".
OL,15,FThe legislation relates to claims on
OL,16,Fproperty stolen by Nazi Germany, then
OL,17,Fseized by Poland's communist regime.
OL,19,FThe law sets a 30-year limit on
OL,20,Fchallenges to such confiscations.
